# Testing conventions

- Unit spec beside implementation: `foo.service.ts` + `foo.service.spec.ts`
- Contract tests: `packages/contracts/src/*.spec.ts`
- E2E: `apps/client/e2e/`, `apps/api` vitest e2e config
- QA writes failing tests before BE/FE implementation (see AGENTS.md)
- Prefer testing behavior over implementation details
